	(text "DENOISIFICATION\n* This system provides a the backbone of a noisefree \n  environment for the delicate phototube signals.\n* The Isolated PSU produces a regulated +/-12V pair \n  for instrumentation and a clean +5V for the digital \n  circuitry.\n* The ISO7762 is a 6ch logic isolater is used to \n  transmit data from the sensing circuit to the \n  microcontroller for processing without interfering \n  with the system."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
